users/user-lifecycle.md
# User Lifecycle Management

## New User

Typical onboarding tasks include:

- Create user account
- Assign Microsoft 365 license
- Add to security groups
- Configure mailbox
- Assign Teams access
- Enroll user device
- Verify MFA registration

---

## Employee Changes

Examples include:

- Department transfer
- Manager update
- License changes
- Group membership updates

---

## Offboarding

Checklist:

- Disable account
- Reset password
- Remove licenses
- Block sign-in
- Remove group memberships
- Archive mailbox (per policy)
- Remove company devices
